title: Surfing America 2014 USA Championships Recap
description: Our under 18 amateur O'Neill surf team blew up at the 2014 USA Championships, down at Lower Trestles. With Sebastian Mendes taking 4th in the boys U12, Noah Hill 3rd in boys U14, and Jake Davis dropping a 2nd in the main division of boys U18.
